  "name": {
    "en": "Gradient",
    "zh": "漸層"
  },
  "desc": {
    "en": "No lamps at all. Every bit of light comes from one huge gradient panel, the most extreme case of an object acting as a light source.",
    "zh": "整組沒有使用任何燈光，光線全部來自一片巨大的漸層發光板，是「物體也能當光源」最極端的例子。"
  },
  "tip": {
    "en": "The two ends of the gradient set the overall colour. Editing them in the material swaps the whole mood without relighting.",
    "zh": "漸層兩端的顏色決定整體色調，改材質裡的顏色就能換掉一整套氛圍，不需要重新佈光。"
  },
  "engine_note": "procedural",
